Title: The 16 best days on my life...
DateModified: '2018-02-20'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/the-16-best-days-on-my-life
SetInCountry: India
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Ritesh Arora
AuthorCountry: India
Text: 'Four driving enthusiasts passionate about driving took up a challenge of driving
  through some of the most adventurous roads, mountains, mountain passes, rivers and
  lakes of India on their dream car XUV 5OO. Three of them Ritesh, Amit and Ashok
  hail from Pune (Maharashtra, India) while the fourth team mate Akash comes from
  the National Capital of India - New Delhi.


  The dream roadtrip was conceived on May 11, 2014 and codenamed "Dream''e''Leh",
  each alphabet of which expands as "D-Dream R-Roadtrip E-Expedition-to A-Adventuresome
  M-Mountains-of e-Exhurb LEH".


  For the detailed story navigate to

  http://dream-e-leh-2014.blogspot.in/2014/06/what-is-dreameleh.html?m=1'
